subject: Basketball (College)
organizations: Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University
lead_paragraph: Vanessa Panousis scored 21 points and shot 5 of 8 from 3-point range as Virginia Tech continued its fast start with a 57-43 upset of No. 8 Tennessee on Sunday.
